patthana16.11:1.1_0: Abyākataṁ lokiyaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā naabyākato nalokiyo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.11:1.1_1: Abyākataṁ lokiyaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā nakusalo nalokiyo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.11:1.1_2: Abyākataṁ lokiyaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā naakusalo nalokiyo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.11:1.1_3: Abyākataṁ lokiyaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā naakusalo nalokiyo ca naabyākato nalokiyo ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā.
patthana16.11:1.1_4: Abyākataṁ lokiyaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā nakusalo nalokiyo ca naakusalo nalokiyo ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā.
patthana16.11:1.1_5: Hetuyā pañca …pe… vipāke tīṇi …pe… avigate pañca.

patthana16.11:3.1_0: Abyākataṁ lokuttaraṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nakusalo nalokuttaro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.11:3.1_1: Abyākataṁ lokuttaraṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naakusalo nalokuttaro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.11:3.1_2: Abyākataṁ lokuttaraṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nakusalo nalokuttaro ca naakusalo nalokuttaro ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā … tīṇi. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
